divs: sighting detailsrunning in a country store left home at 5:45am noticed red and white lights in the distance thinking it was a new tower when i pulled in parking lot it kept coming closer, slowly passing over i saw a square shaped object with white and red lights on each corner saw something of rings maybe, on the bottom or circles for design, engine i'm not sure could also see the rim of the side. higher than the trees going toward the dam in a southwesterly direction i got the store manager then the cashier came out we watched it slowly going away. we were surprised how close with no noise, and the shape being square it seemed odd looked up on the internet and saw others saw something close to what i'd seen. 12\30\11 just at dawn no sunshine yet sky was light enough to really make the object stand out i didn't have zoom on my phone camera
